{"tid":2033834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我自橫刀向天笑，去留肝膽兩崑崙","createTime":"2020-05-25T01:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:24:34.000Z","uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff7fbea1aa58a4e44ef78c9ad9d5e4ca58dc2b3","tid":2033834,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:43:48.000Z","msg":"望門投止思張儉，忍死須臾待杜根；我自橫刀向天笑，去留肝膽兩崑崙。<br />\n<br />\n意思是逃亡的生活如此緊張，看到有人家就要上門投宿，我希望出逃的康有為梁啓超等人能夠像張儉一樣受到人們的保護，也希望戰友們能如杜根一樣繼續維新大業。<br />\n<br />\n你我肝膽相照，光明磊落，如崑崙山一樣有雄偉的氣魄，是死是活又有什麼重要呢。"},{"pid":"dd06c0fdce9fee1e1c51f4923c81d7e893cd1eb0","tid":2033834,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:44:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/3bnmx6a.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2F3bnmx6a.html&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=4e9d7e51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/3bnmx6a.html</a>"},{"pid":"bc52b3487da44988271875cd94b85230b792193a","tid":2033834,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}